{"tid":905410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"APEC峰會彭斯：加倍徵稅　 習近平：保護主義注定失敗","createTime":"2018-11-17T05:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T08:04:02.000Z","uid":13663,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a2351652dd1a25fa712eaa6b3992ed8add86b6","tid":905410,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"彭斯維持他過去多個星期以來對中國的「戰鬥格」。他在會上重申，針對北京「重商主義」（mercantilism）的貿易政策（即追求國家最大程度的富足與強盛，國內留下最多的經濟活動的方針），以及知識產權盜竊問題，揚言華府的打擊行動不會鬆手。<br />\n<br />\n他還威脅華府可能會加倍徵收關稅，迫使中國讓步。此番強硬論調跟美國總統特朗普周五（16日）說法有出入，特朗普說相信中國有心想達成協議，美國未必再向中國徵收更多關稅。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯還批評中國在全球大起基建，稱其中許多項目質量差劣，並令發展中國家背負無法負擔的債務。<br />\n<br />\n他還宣布，美國將加入盟友澳洲的一項計劃，共同開發巴布亞新畿內亞的海軍基地。這裏正是峰會舉行的地方，中方亦提供援助及貸款，爭取巴布亞新幾內亞的基建項目。"},{"pid":"40090dfe138aea73227b4ef4b6d76edd30beaa4f","tid":905410,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"另一邊廂，首先發言的習近平則表示，保護主義和單邊主義使世界經濟增長蒙上陰影，揚言保護主義注定會失敗。他強調支持全球自由貿易體系，並反擊外界對中國一帶一路項目的批評，指這不是排除非成員的專享俱樂部，亦不是一個債務陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n習近平說，「人類再次走到一個十字路口，我們應該選擇哪個方向？合作還是對抗？開啟或是關閉大門？互利共贏還是零和遊戲？」"},{"pid":"425ac6b32aedc0f029e68ab3736adae12b4c5040","tid":905410,"uid":13663,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dxNkG2n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdxNkG2n.png&h=4ec2208b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4601a304078677126a5c7a912033d11d5dbbaba3","tid":905410,"uid":31946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"侵話唔會加，彭斯就話加<br />\n<br />\n就黎精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf1649a372b8d8b97ab66bb1fccdb88a5613f86","tid":905410,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"425ac6b32aedc0f029e68ab3736adae12b4c5040","tid":905410,"uid":13663,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dxNkG2n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdxNkG2n.png&h=4ec2208b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef1c5bf4e124a3eb0b2ff1461ef2c826b927e1f","tid":905410,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4601a304078677126a5c7a912033d11d5dbbaba3","tid":905410,"uid":31946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"侵話唔會加，彭斯就話加<br />\n<br />\n就黎精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"到底信邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f05ef47b1fd37607dacc5aad4af08e965e20f62","tid":905410,"uid":121580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"支國個主義就係不守承諾主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c5ed7a51dd9717d4f356f9cb46f57563984c51","tid":905410,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a91ab802cec506c01f8621fe3d5fd30a5868ef1","tid":905410,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:42:05.000Z","msg":"糖果與鞭子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278f3ebf3c71052f2673c4ebca37e35dd373fcdc","tid":905410,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"3f05ef47b1fd37607dacc5aad4af08e965e20f62","tid":905410,"uid":121580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"支國個主義就係不守承諾主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"而家似係美國wow"},{"pid":"595d908cf6c7f41a903d67fba1ceacc1733a35fa","tid":905410,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:44:29.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普周五說中國已向美國提出一系列願意採取的措施，以解決美中貿易衝突，美國政府可能不需進一步向中國貨加徵關稅，但他又說，他仍認為情況不可接受。而副總統彭斯出席亞太經合組織會議時亦重申，除非中國改變貿易政策，不然美方不會撤銷關稅措施，並狠轟中國不透明的「金錢外交」手段。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮說：「中國希望達成協議，他們提出一份清單，一份頗長的清單，列出願意做的事，但我仍不接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」他表示清單中有142個項目，「頗為完整」，但「仍遺漏了4、5個主要事項」。他又說：「我想我們或可一併爭取到這些。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普向價值2500億美元(1.95萬億港元)的中國進口商品徵收關稅，迫使中國改變貿易行為，他警告若北京政府不從，美國將向中國其餘2670億美元(2.08萬億港元)商品徵收關稅。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說：「我們可能不需這樣做，中國希望達成協議。」<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"7ed99e860290c04d96296ccb38bc83729146ac8a","tid":905410,"uid":44458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"習真係可鄰，肯定幾個月晚晚訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1b6af255c80b8cd334b25f89c762eadefa9309","tid":905410,"uid":41545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:48:23.000Z","msg":"小學雞點解要自己咒返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c26648ae5e83fedb80c9a5ca18468facde08082","tid":905410,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ed99e860290c04d96296ccb38bc83729146ac8a","tid":905410,"uid":44458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"習真係可鄰，肯定幾個月晚晚訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:49:31.000Z","msg":"獨裁者點會瞓唔到，草民食一年草都唔會動搖到佢地位，你估金正恩會唔會瞓唔到？"},{"pid":"f4636a81900dcaa2148da8a8e6c9dc5c